 - Yes.

24
00:02:07,410 --> 00:02:12,130
This simulation will strengthen your ability to respond to an IED.

25
00:02:12,130 --> 00:02:17,220
And in order to learn the on-site inspection function, with the support of the Air Force's EOD,

26
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:21,540
our police station's PBI Team (Post Blast Investigation) will simulate

27
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:25,390
the terrorist incidents that are recently occurring frequently in southeast Asia.

28
00:02:25,390 --> 00:02:29,640
Today Eugene Hathaway, an FBI terrorist specialist

29
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:34,660
will personally supervise the test.

30
00:02:43,850 --> 00:02:48,470
An IED, Improvised Explosive Device,

31
