33
00:02:58,190 --> 00:03:01,680
We're using beef and blood, which I'm placing here

34
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:05,830
in order to test how and how far human tissue and blood

35
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:07,990
are scattered by an IED explosion.

36
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,090
The explosive that I'm going to use is an ANFO,

37
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:15,010
a mixture of ammonium nitrate and diesel.

38
00:03:15,010 --> 00:03:17,290
It's typical of homemade bombs.

39
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:20,940
