40
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:24,180
will be placed here around the explosive.

41
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:29,070
You remember the incident at the Boston Marathon in the US in 2013, right?

42
00:03:29,070 --> 00:03:34,840
There were many casualties because of metal beads placed in a pressure cooker.

43
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,990
What about Korea?

44
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:41,040
Do you say that terrorism has a remote chance in this country?

45
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:51,780
Explode it!

46
00:03:55,370 --> 00:03:57,240
 Bomb Disposal Unit

47
