Bomb! Bomb!

48
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:01,380
Bomb!

49
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:12,220
 Post Bomb Investigation

50
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:19,700
Awesome! Wow!

51
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:24,500
The force was incredible. An ANFO is so powerful.

52
00:04:27,950 --> 00:04:32,480
Someday this image will become real in the middle of Seoul.

53
